{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BB-WHATS-INCLUDED INNER (no accordion wrapper)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Renders one What's Included category — a sub-heading followed by the
product list — without wrapping it in a <details> element.

Used inside a single outer accordion in product-info.liquid so all
categories live under ONE expand/collapse instead of ten separate ones.

Parameters:
  * product         — product object
  * name            — category display name (e.g. "The Liquor")
  * metafield_name  — namespace key under product.metafields.custom

Returns nothing visible if the product has no value for the metafield.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign metafield_value = product.metafields.custom[metafield_name] -%}
{%- if metafield_value != blank -%}
  <div class="bb-wi-category">
    <h4 class="bb-wi-category__title">{{ name | escape }}</h4>
    <div class="bb-wi-category__items">
      {%- for item in metafield_value.value -%}
        {%- assign product_ref = item.product.value -%}
        {%- assign quantity = item.quantity.value -%}
        {%- if product_ref -%}
          <div class="bb-wi-item">
            {%- if product_ref.featured_media -%}
              <img
                class="bb-wi-item__image"
                src="{{ product_ref.featured_media | image_url: width: 80 }}"
                srcset="{{ product_ref.featured_media | image_url: width: 60 }} 60w, {{ product_ref.featured_media | image_url: width: 80 }} 80w, {{ product_ref.featured_media | image_url: width: 120 }} 120w"
                sizes="40px"
                width="40"
                height="40"
                loading="lazy"
                alt="{{ product_ref.title | escape }}">
            {%- endif -%}
            <span class="bb-wi-item__label">
              {%- if quantity and quantity > 1 -%}<span class="bb-wi-item__qty">{{ quantity }}×</span> {% endif -%}
              {{ product_ref.title | escape }}
            </span>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
